OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover failure to stop       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fradicalisation             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The prison service has failed to       
OL,6, recognise the dangers Islamist gangs   
OL,7, and convicted terrorists pose inside   
OL,8, jail, a report warns.                  
OL,10,FThe independent reviewer of terrorist  
OL,11,Flegislation, Jonathan Hall QC, said    
OL,12,Fprisons must not provide opportunities 
OL,13,Ffor militants to plan new attacks.     
OL,15,FBut the service had "lost its role in  
OL,16,Fthe national endeavour to reduce the   
OL,17,Frisk of terrorism".                    
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Justice said it was    
OL,20,Fcommitted to isolating radicalisers.   
